able to invest it?

00:47:08.200 --> 00:47:09.220
JONATHAN GRUBER: Well,
actually, it's interesting.

00:47:09.220 --> 00:47:10.780
It depends on the
form of financial aid.

00:47:10.780 --> 00:47:10.990
Why?

00:47:10.990 --> 00:47:12.370
Someone tell me why it's
dependent on the form

00:47:12.370 --> 00:47:13.540
